## NotificationContext Usage

Always use NotificationContext for user feedback instead of console.log/alert():

```typescript
import { useNotification } from "../contexts/NotificationContext";
const { showNotification } = useNotification();

// Usage examples
showNotification("error", `Erro ao carregar: ${error.message}`);
showNotification("success", "Operação realizada com sucesso!");
showNotification("warning", "Selecione um item para continuar");
showNotification("info", "Funcionalidade ainda não implementada");
```

**Guidelines:**
- Use specific error messages with `error.message` when available
- Choose appropriate levels: error, success, warning, info
- Always provide feedback for user actions (save, delete, transfer, etc.)
- Use Portuguese for all user-facing messages
